## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e7389-114">此构造函数在包含语法中创建对 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 对象的规则引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-114">This constructor creates a rule reference to an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object within the containing  grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-115">若要创建对外部语法文件中的 `rule` 元素的规则引用，请使用以下任何构造函数：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-115">To create a rule reference to a `rule` element in an external grammar file, use any of the following constructors:</span></span>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e7389-116">下面的示例创建一个语法，用于识别 "已赢得世界杯的国家" 的短语，后跟赢得世界杯的国家/地区的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-116">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-117">创建 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 对象 `winnerRule` 并为其提供字符串标识符 `WorldCupWinner`后，该示例会将 "已赢得世界杯的全国" 这一字符串追加到该规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-117">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example appends the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-118">该示例使用 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 对象生成一个欧洲国家/地区列表和一个南亚国家/地区列表，并将每个列表添加到其各自的规则中 `ruleEurope` 或 `ruleSAmerica`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-118">Using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects, the example then builds a list of European countries/regions and a list of South American countries/regions, and adds each list to its respective rule, `ruleEurope` or `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-119">然后，该示例为 `ruleEurope` 和 `ruleSAmerica` 创建规则引用，并将其添加到 `WorldCupWinner` 规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-119">The example then creates rule references for `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica` and adds them to the `WorldCupWinner` rule.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e7389-120">创建的语法采用以下形式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-120">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England </item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e7389-125">此构造函数创建对外部语法文件的规则引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-125">This constructor creates a rule reference to an external grammar file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-126">URI 还可以包含要引用的规则的标识符，例如 `http://www.contoso.com/ExternalGrammar.grxml#targetRule`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-126">The URI may also include the identifier of a rule to reference, for example `http://www.contoso.com/ExternalGrammar.grxml#targetRule`.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="e7389-127">如果 `uri` 参数未指定规则标识符，则规则引用指向目标语法的根规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-127">If the `uri` parameter does not specify a rule identifier, the rule reference points to the root rule of the target grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-128">若要在同一语法中创建对 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 对象的规则引用，请使用以下任何构造函数：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-128">To create a rule reference to an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object within the same grammar, use any of the following constructors:</span></span>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e7389-129">下面的示例创建一个应用程序的语法，该语法返回有关 bus 往复服务的信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-129">The following example creates a grammar for an application that returns information about bus shuttle service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-130">第一种方法 `GrammarUrlForRoute`采用指定路由的字符串，并将其追加到指定语法位置的字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-130">The first method, `GrammarUrlForRoute`, takes a string that specifies a route and appends it to a string specifying the location of a grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-131">这将指定该语法中的特定规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-131">This specifies a particular rule in that grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-132">方法返回该规则的 `Uri`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-132">The method returns a `Uri` for that rule.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e7389-133">第二种方法 `CreateGrammarForRoute`，它将创建一个名为 `grammar` 的 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 元素，该元素具有由 `GrammarUrlForRoute`传递给它的 `Uri` 指定的规则引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-133">The second method, `CreateGrammarForRoute`, creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> element named `grammar` with a rule reference specified by the `Uri` passed to it by `GrammarUrlForRoute`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-134">请注意，名为 _route 的变量是封闭类的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-134">Note that the variable named _route is a member of an enclosing class.</span></span>  
  
```  
private Uri GrammarUrlForRoute(string route)  
{  
  return new Uri("http://localhost/MyBus/MyBusLocations.grxml#LocationsForRoute" + route);  
}  
  
private SrgsDocument CreateGrammarForRoute()  
{  
  SrgsDocument grammar = new SrgsDocument();  
  grammar.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Voice;  
  SrgsRule rule = new SrgsRule("LocationsForRoute" + _route);  
  SrgsRuleRef ruleref = new SrgsRuleRef(GrammarUrlForRoute(_route));  
  
  SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag tag = new SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag ("$.Location = $$");  
  
  rule.Elements.Add(ruleref);  
  rule.Elements.Add(tag);  
  grammar.Rules.Add(rule);  
  grammar.Root = rule;  
  return grammar;  
}  
```  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="e7389-135">在前面的示例中未声明并未定义名为 _ 的变量`route`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-135">The variable named _`route` is undeclared and undefined in the preceding sample.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e7389-136">它应声明为 <xref:System.String>，并在编译和运行前面的示例之前，包含特定总线路由的路由号。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7389-136">It should be declared as a <xref:System.String> and contain the route number for a particular bus route before the preceding sample is compiled and run.</span></span>

  
  
